data.description: Nestled in one of the most sought-after areas of San Fernando within the City of Los Angeles, this delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home (with a total of 4 bedrooms) offers a perfect opportunity for a 1st time homebuyer. Conveniently situated just minutes away from Mission College, Veterans Park, El Cariso Park/Golf Course, restaurants, shopping centers, and schools, it also provides easy access to the 5, 118, 405, 210, 134, and 14 freeways.  Notable upgrades include central AC/heat, a newer tankless water heater, copper plumbing, and a roof that was recently installed in 2021. Ideal for those seeking an affordable opportunity in the San Fernando Valley, this home is move-in ready. The garage has been transformed into 2 additional bedrooms, a flexible space that can easily be converted back or adapted into a permitted ADU. Property is ready for the new owner. This is a Single Family Home - NO HOA!!!
